## Example Entries

### Decision Log Entry
```
Date: 2025-01-15
Decision: Use LangChain for agent orchestration
Rationale: Provides built-in agent framework, tool integration, and async support
Alternatives: Custom implementation, other frameworks
Impact: All agent implementations, tool integrations
```

### Pattern Entry
```
Pattern: Agent Tool Creation
Context: Creating tools for LangChain agents
Code:
  @tool
  def my_tool(input: str) -> str:
      """Tool description."""
      return result
When to Use: When creating reusable agent capabilities
```

### Learning Entry
```
Date: 2025-01-15
Learning: LangChain agents need explicit tool descriptions
Context: Agent wasn't using tools correctly
Solution: Added detailed descriptions to all tools
Application: All future tool definitions
```

